# Already self-documents (line 1 comment). A header may be added:
# Purpose: Deny-all ignore; every tracked path must be explicitly allowlisted below.
# Role: config
# Micro-container candidate: no (VCS ignore config, not gate logic)
# Note: keep the existing leading-** deny rule first; place header above it.

# Default-deny: every tracked file must be explicitly allowlisted below.
**

!*/
